description:
As a Ranger of Azuria, it's your duty to save endangered monster species from extinction. Through Habitat restoration, save and restore monster numbers and with your conservation efforts, discover new monstie companions. 

Your story begins March 13, 2026 on Xbox Series X|S.

Pre-order Monster Hunter Stories 3: Twisted Reflection now.
